# Global configuration section
#   Values here are used as defaults for any following Channel section that
#   doesn't specify them.
Expunge None
Create Both

MaildirStore local
Path ~/Mail/
SubFolders Verbatim
Inbox ~/Mail/work/Inbox
Trash ~/Mail/WorkDeleted


IMAPStore work
Host localhost
User ymohammad
PassCmd "pass show exchange-script"
SSLType None
AuthMechs LOGIN
Port 1143
Timeout 180
