Channel work
Far :work:
Near :local:WorkYusuf
Expunge Both
Create Near
Sync PullNew Push
Pattern Inbox* Sent* Draft* Deleted*
CopyArrivalDate yes


MaildirStore PetroleumUnit
Path ~/Mail/PetroleumUnit
SubFolders Verbatim
Inbox ~/Mail/PetroleumUnit/Inbox
Trash ~/Mail/PetroleumUnit/Deleted
MaxSize 1m


IMAPStore petroleum_unit
Host localhost
User petroleum.unit
PassCmd "pass show mbsync/petroleum.unit"
SSLType None
AuthMechs LOGIN
Port 1143
Timeout 180

Channel PetroleumUnit
Far :petroleum_unit:
Near :PetroleumUnit:
Expunge Both
Create Near
Sync PullNew Push
Pattern Inbox* Sent* Draft* Deleted*
CopyArrivalDate yes

